---
const phoneNumber = "59164278427";
const whatsappMsg = "Hola,%20quiero%20sorprender%20a%20mam%C3%A1%20con%20Chocolates%20Taboada";
---

<section id="comprar" class="relative py-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-warm-white to-soft-pink/60 text-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Glowing visual elements -->
  <div class="absolute w-[350px] h-[350px] left-[10%] top-[10%] rounded-full bg-radial from-gold-premium/8 to-transparent filter blur-2xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute w-[400px] h-[400px] right-[5%] bottom-[10%] rounded-full bg-radial from-satin-pink/10 to-transparent filter blur-2xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <!-- CTA Card -->
    <div class="rounded-[42px] px-6 py-14 md:p-16 border border-rose-wine/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-white to-[#F4CADC] shadow-[0_30px_90px_rgba(122,30,77,0.14)] relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Inner Glow -->
      <div class="absolute w-72 h-72 -left-20 -top-20 rounded-full bg-radial from-gold-premium/20 to-transparent filter blur-md pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-berry-dark leading-tight relative z-10">
        Resuelve el regalo con elegancia
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-dark-chocolate/72 max-w-xl mx-auto mt-5 mb-8 relative z-10">
        Haz que mamá reciba algo que se vea verdaderamente especial, se sienta premium desde el empaque y se recuerde con el cariño de un gran momento.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Big Golden CTA Button -->
      <div class="relative z-10 inline-block">
        <a 
          href={`https://wa.me/${phoneNumber}?text=${whatsappMsg}`}
          target="_blank" 
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 min-h-[56px] px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-extrabold text-dark-chocolate bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-premium via-[#F6D983] to-champagne-gold shadow-[0_18px_42px_rgba(212,175,55,0.3),_inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.5)] overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:brightness-[1.04] hover:shadow-[0_24px_58px_rgba(212,175,55,0.4)] transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          <!-- Shimmer shine effect -->
          <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/55 to-transparent -translate-x-[130%] group-hover:animate-shimmer"></span>
          💝 Quiero sorprender a mamá
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
